header.gameNote: FRONTIER COMMUNICATIONS AMERICAN ATHLETIC CONFERENCE WOMEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP - QUARTERFINAL

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson takes the entry pass and makes the layup after drawing the contact as UConn leads Tulsa early.
videos.headline: UConn's Samuelson converts 3-point play

videos.description: UConn's Crystal Dangerfield finds Gabby Williams down low for the and-1 layup to extend their lead over Tulsa.
videos.headline: Great feed leads to bucket for Huskies

videos.description: UConn's Napheesa Collier comes up with the steal and then finds Gabby Williams in stride for the wide open layup against Tulsa.
videos.headline: UConn turns steal into easy points

videos.description: UConn's Gabby Williams creates the turnover before Crystal Dangerfield finds Napheesa Collier in transition for the and-1 layup to cap off the huge first half against Tulsa.
videos.headline: Turnover leads to fancy finish for UConn
